It will be updated as the class progresses.
Detailed syllabus and lecture notes can be found [here](http://cs20.stanford.edu).
For this course, I use python3.6 and TensorFlow 1.4.1. For the code and notes of the previous year's course, please see the folder 2017 and the website https://web.stanford.edu/class/cs20si/2017 For setup instruction and the list of dependencies, please see the setup folder of this repository.
